<HEADLINE> State Fair continues record-breaking pace  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   SYRACUSE, N.Y. (AP) - The New York State Fair concluded the
first third of its 12-day run with attendance numbers on a
record-breaking pace.
</P>
<P>
