<HEADLINE> Vikings Reach Deal With Dishman  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   MINNEAPOLIS (AP) -- The Minnesota Vikings reached a contract
agreement Sunday night with veteran cornerback Cris Dishman, who
was cut earlier in the day by the Kansas City Chiefs.
</P>
<P>
   As originally reported by CNNSI.com, Dishman agreed to terms
with Minnesota.
</P>
<P>
